data.description: Single level 3 bedroom, 2 full bath home with an open living area.  Features living room with propane fireplace, great room, Eat-In kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and backsplash.  Large .64 acre lot, plenty of room for RV or boat storage.  Metal roof put on in 2016, HVAC 2016.  There is a pond on the back of the lot and it is only .6 miles to the Hagley Boat Landing.  If you are looking for privacy and no Homeowners Association, see today.
